project.name: StreetComplete
project.description: Surveyor app for Android - this listing mentions tags can be added by this editor using quests (overlays are not supported for now in this listing, please open an issue at https://github.com/matkoniecz/Zazolc/issues if you care about this - or upvote one that exists if created already). Tags used for filtering or ones that can be removed during editing are not listed. Tags from iD presets and Name Suggestion Index that can be used while adding new shops are also not listed - see https://taginfo.openstreetmap.org/projects/id_editor and https://taginfo.openstreetmap.org/projects/name_suggestion_index for tag listings.
